Package: AdaRMST
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jinghao", "Sun", , "jinghao.sun.io@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The goal of AdaRMST is to implement a set of novel adaptive restricted mean survival time methods for clinical trials, especially under non-proportional hazards. See the methodology paper: Jinghao Sun, Douglas E. Schaubel, Eric J. Tchetgen Tchetgen (2025). Beyond Fixed Restriction Time: Adaptive Restricted Mean Survival Time Methods in Clinical Trials.
